{"tid":1938441,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英媒：王室助理確診　英女王提早往溫莎堡","createTime":"2020-03-22T14:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T00:00:57.000Z","uid":209657,"like":158,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"b324f9c24023f1c0b86874a19b5b63a04f5c4db6","tid":1938441,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/20200322/318515751143215104.jpeg/YcUwlxz0Pdw11j1GBsEy0qcxDhXCq96XZ3RRBGd0UQQ?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F20200322%2F318515751143215104.jpeg%2FYcUwlxz0Pdw11j1GBsEy0qcxDhXCq96XZ3RRBGd0UQQ%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=3d4b1ac9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b2f3910643742a1346617c1df557d55d8c07436","tid":1938441,"uid":209657,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎的英國死亡個案增加，英國媒體3月21日報道，英國白金漢宮有王室助理確診，導致英國女王伊麗莎白二世（Queen Elizabeth II）19日離開白金漢宮，前往溫莎堡居住。<br />\n<br />\n這位姓名沒有被披露的助理，相信是在上周較早時生病及確診的。據報這位染疫的助理已在康復中。暫時未知道這位助理的工作與英女王的接觸有多密切，但所有與這位已確診助理有接觸的王室職員都已在自我隔離。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指她離開白金漢宮到溫莎堡度假，這個安排較以往為早。她離開白金漢宮據報是為安全計的安排。王室消息人士稱，英女王健康良好，她與丈夫菲臘親王都在避免與其他人接觸。外界預期她與他會在可見的將來留在溫莎堡。"},{"pid":"6db8d8a99f260ab4423f233423ac6f1f15d31f6e","tid":1938441,"uid":155095,"like":173,"dislike":8,"score":165,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ct.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/H3BFlp_jtrNbGS9XvRDMGw--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD0xODY3O3E9ODU7cm90YXRlPWF1dG87dz0xNDAw/https://s.yimg.com/ob/image/e30713c7-e761-4d8b-92c0-905ca111cadd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fct.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FH3BFlp_jtrNbGS9XvRDMGw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD0xODY3O3E9ODU7cm90YXRlPWF1dG87dz0xNDAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fob%2Fimage%2Fe30713c7-e761-4d8b-92c0-905ca111cadd.jpg&h=6902bf13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47d2ad2f3d4dd9b99d071ce109c4d25463513d9b","tid":1938441,"uid":209657,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"英國《太陽報》在3月21日引述消息人士說：「這位員工在英女王前往溫莎堡前，其樣本已在測試中呈陽性反應。但王室有500名員工，跟所有辦公場所一樣，不難想像在某程度上會造成影響。」<br />\n<br />\n英國白金漢宮拒絕就有員工確診置評，但稱已採取所有必需的步驟防疫。"},{"pid":"4cfef8a9ddb3276e922a8416d95f2c5c35e42e0b","tid":1938441,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86820de3ad8cb851a691099b58fd4fb84bc1164e","tid":1938441,"uid":79563,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"女皇有無屌柒BJ?"},{"pid":"80da2560db33d368b9e60afe8617a05d7563f1d8","tid":1938441,"uid":129739,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"女王同親王會唔會因為咁而&hellip;"},{"pid":"d12604b2019861703e1067d7043b0f22be3383f9","tid":1938441,"uid":51469,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"herd immunity即<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34058be6e9e8e700c338b6c7aa3b90f3b99728c8","tid":1938441,"uid":123189,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:19:29.000Z","msg":"英女皇份工做d乜架?"},{"pid":"a836669f181009a1dc13dcd34aea23e2398d5629","tid":1938441,"uid":109102,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:20:21.000Z","msg":"god bless the queen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2de4ecfb17802cf09f3afd4b5950692082da76f","tid":1938441,"uid":133977,"like":8,"dislike":109,"score":-101,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"其實佢驚咩<br />\n 都就死嫁啦"},{"pid":"560a0f9811963dd3b3a395ac7dd097748657c898","tid":1938441,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"86820de3ad8cb851a691099b58fd4fb8